name: Obi-Wan, Crazy Wizard
Lore: '''That old man''s just a crazy wizard.'' Obi-Wan lived in Tatooine''s deserts for years...ready for the right moment to act.',
Text: 'Old Ben is a Used Interrupt and may target this site even if not a Tatooine site. Dark Jedi may not ''swing'' lightsabers more than once per battle here. When leaving table, place all your cards on Obi-Wan in Used Pile. Immune to attrition < 5.',
